00:41:25,276 --> 00:41:27,987
Because if you had gone up there
to check out my girlfriend,

759
00:41:28,112 --> 00:41:29,947
you wouldn't have come
back here and lied to me about it.

760
00:41:30,072 --> 00:41:31,490
You would have thrown
her right in my face.

761
00:41:31,615 --> 00:41:34,118
You underestimate the
entertainment value of your obsessions.

762
00:41:34,243 --> 00:41:37,746
And then there were all those calls
you weren't taking in front of me.

763
00:41:40,249 --> 00:41:42,793
So I dialed the number of the calls
you weren't taking.

764
00:41:42,918 --> 00:41:44,587
You're seeing a psychiatrist.

765
00:41:54,889 --> 00:41:57,474
You had no right to
invade my privacy.

766
00:41:59,226 --> 00:42:01,645
- Is that?
- Yeah, it's irony.

767
00:42:03,439 --> 00:42:04,607
Hey.

768
00:42:07,234 --> 00:42:10,613
God sent you.

769
00:42:12,364 --> 00:42:15,159
Suddenly, you're not
so fascinating.

770
00:42:18,370 --> 00:42:20,664
You're spying on your team?

771
00:42:20,789 --> 00:42:22,541
Prioritize, Wilson.

772
00:42:22,666 --> 00:42:24,835
Is that really what you want
to torture me about right now?

773
00:42:24,960 --> 00:42:26,170
I don't want to torture
you at all.

774
00:42:26,295 --> 00:42:27,495
I think this is a great thing,

775
00:42:27,588 --> 00:42:30,674
not something you have to drive an hour
out of town to shroud in mystery.

776
00:42:30,799 --> 00:42:32,635
Yeah, whining on
someone's couch

777
00:42:32,760 --> 00:42:34,595
is an excellent use of my time.

778
00:42:34,720 --> 00:42:36,800
Maybe I'll discover
that my childhood wasn't perfect.

779
00:42:36,847 --> 00:42:39,516
So your attitude
about therapy clearly hasn't changed.

780
00:42:39,642 --> 00:42:41,477
And yet you went.

781
00:42:41,602 --> 00:42:44,480
Which leads me to believe that maybe
something else has changed.

782
00:42:44,605 --> 00:42:48,359
Maybe you think you can change.
Credit Cuddy with that.

783
00:42:48,484 --> 00:42:51,320
Not much credit to
take 'cause I'm not going back.

784
00:42:51,445 --> 00:42:53,072
Oh, House, please.

785
00:42:53,739 --> 00:42:55,574
I assume you went
because you're tired of screwing up

786
00:42:55,699 --> 00:42:57,409
every chance you
get at happiness.

787
00:42:57,534 --> 00:42:58,535
Delete contact.

788
00:42:59,078 --> 00:43:01,121
Do not let the fact
that I found out about it...

789
00:43:01,247 --> 00:43:02,915
Don't beat yourself up.

790
00:43:03,165 --> 00:43:05,668
I'm not going back
because it doesn't work.

791
00:43:10,339 --> 00:43:11,674
You'll end up alone.

